column1: SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass, mp3d.e_log_Mass AS mpMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas AS mpMGerr,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift AS mp_z, s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 500000

as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR, mp3d.plateifu, mdap.plateifu,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on (mdap.plateifu = mp3d.plateifu AND mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR, mp3d.plateifu, mdap.plateifu,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on (mdap.plateifu = mp3d.plateifu AND mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec)  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50, mdap.plateifu, mp3d.plateifu,  mdap.ifudesign, mp3d.ifudsgn HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

 p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR, mp3d.plateifu, mdap.plateifu,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on (mdap.plateifu = mp3d.plateifu AND mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec)  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50, mdap.plateifu, mp3d.plateifu,  mdap.ifudesign, mp3d.ifudsgn HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

SELECT p.objid, p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.err_u,p.err_g,p.err_r,p.err_i,p.err_z, s.specobjid,s.class,s.z as redshift, count(*) OVER() FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  WHERE p.r BETWEEN 0 AND 23 AND s.class = 'GALAXY' ORDER BY p.objid  limit 10

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass, mp3d.e_log_Mass AS mpMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas AS mpMGerr,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift AS mp_z, s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 limit 500000

SELECT  count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  LEFT JOIN zooSpec AS Z ON Z.specobjid = s.specobjid  LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS elp ON elp.specobjid = s.specobjid  LEFT JOIN nsatlas AS ns ON ns.z = s.z WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.fracDev_r BETWEEN 0 AND 0.1  AND Z.p_cs_debiased >= 0.8  AND z.spiral = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND ns.sersic_mass > 0  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND ns.sersic_n < 6  AND elp.EW_Ha_6562 > 0 and elp.EW_Ha_6562 < 1

SELECT  count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  LEFT JOIN zooSpec AS Z ON Z.specobjid = s.specobjid  LEFT JOIN emissionLinesPort AS elp ON elp.specobjid = s.specobjid  LEFT JOIN nsatlas AS ns ON ns.z = s.z WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.fracDev_r BETWEEN 0 AND 0.1  AND Z.p_cs_debiased >= 0.8  AND z.spiral = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND ns.sersic_mass > 0  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND ns.sersic_n < 6  AND elp.EW_Ha_6562 > 0

SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN GalSpecLine AS L ON s.SpecObjID = L.SpecObjID  WHERE   (S.class = 'GALAXY' or S.class = 'QSO') and SNmedian > 10 and   L.h_beta_flux > 3* L.h_beta_flux_err and  L.h_alpha_flux > 3* L.h_alpha_flux_err and  L.oiii_5007_flux > 3* L.oiii_5007_flux_err and   L.nii_6584_flux > 3* L.nii_6584_flux and   L.sii_6717_flux > 3* L.sii_6717_flux and   (S.z BETWEEN 0.01 and 0.5) and   S.zwarning = 0

SELECT COUNT(p.objid) AS Ct, MAX(p.psfMag_z) AS Mag,  cast(p.ra/5 as int)*5.0 as ra,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec FROM PhotoTag AS p  INNER JOIN  (SELECT MIN(q.psfMag_z) AS MZ,  cast(ra/5 as int)*5.0 as ra,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec  FROM PhotoTag as q WHERE   (q.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (q.type = 6) AND  (q.psfMag_z > -9999)  GROUP BY cast(ra/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0   ) AS p1 ON p1.ra=(cast(p.ra/5 as int)*5.0)  AND p1.dec = (cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0) WHERE   (p.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (p.type = 6) AND  (p.psfMag_z < p1.MZ+1) GROUP BY cast(p.ra/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0  ORDER BY cast(p.ra/5 as int)*5.0

SELECT COUNT(p.objid) AS Ct, MAX(p.psfMag_z) AS Mag,  cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec FROM PhotoTag AS p  INNER JOIN  (SELECT MIN(q.psfMag_z) AS MZ,  cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec  FROM PhotoTag as q WHERE   (q.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (q.type = 6) AND  (q.psfMag_z > -9999)  GROUP BY cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0   ) AS p1 ON p1.raCosDec=(cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0) AND p1.dec = (cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0) WHERE   (p.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (p.type = 6) AND  (p.psfMag_z < p1.MZ+1) GROUP BY cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0  ORDER BY cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0

SELECT COUNT(p.objid), MAX(p.psfMag_z),  cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec FROM PhotoTag AS p  INNER JOIN  (SELECT MIN(q.psfMag_z) AS MZ,  cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0 as raCosDec,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0 as dec  FROM PhotoTag as q WHERE   (q.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (q.type = 6) AND  (q.psfMag_z > -9999)  GROUP BY cast((ra/cos(cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(dec/5 as int)*5.0   ) AS p1 ON p1.raCosDec=(cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0) AND p1.dec = (cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0) WHERE   (p.dec BETWEEN 70 AND 75) AND  (p.type = 6) AND  (p.psfMag_z < p1.MZ+1) GROUP BY cast((p.ra/cos(cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0))/5 as int)*5.0,  cast(p.dec/5 as int)*5.0

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR, mp3d.plate, mdap.plate,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50, mdap.plate, mp3d.plate HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r,   s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

SELECT  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median AS mMass, pcam.mstellar_err AS mMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass AS mpMass, mp3d.e_log_Mass AS mpMerr,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas AS mpMassGas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas AS mpMGerr,  pcam.vdisp_median AS mVD, pcam.vdisp_err AS mVDerr,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift AS mp_z, s.z AS Sredshift, pz.z AS Predshift, s.zErr AS SredshiftErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r AS AbsMag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50 AS specSFR, g.sfr_tot_p50 AS SFR,  COUNT(*) as CNT FROM mangaPipe3D as mp3d  JOIN mangaDAPall as mdap on mdap.objra = mp3d.objra AND mdap.objdec = mp3d.objdec  JOIN mangatarget as mtar on mtar.mangaID = mtar.mangaID  JOIN nsatlas as nsa on nsa.nsaid = mtar.nsa_nsaid  JOIN SpecObjAll as s on s.z = nsa.z  JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM11 as pcam on pcam.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN photoz as pz on pz.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = s.specObjID  JOIN galSpecExtra as g on g.specObjID = s.specObjID  JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on p.objID = s.bestObjID WHERE   s.z BETWEEN 0.00 AND 0.15  AND p.devRadErr_r BETWEEN 0.00000000000000000001 AND 100  AND p.devRad_r > 0  AND p.fracDev_r > 0.9  AND Z.p_cs_debiased <= 0.3  AND z.elliptical = 1  AND s.class = 'galaxy'  AND nsa.sersic_ba > 0.85  AND s.velDisp > 0  AND pcam.vdisp_median > 0  AND pcam.mstellar_median >= 10.4  AND pcam.warning = 0  AND g.specsfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND g.sfr_tot_p50 > -9999  AND nsa.sersic_n BETWEEN 3 AND 5.5  AND nsa.sersic_absmag_r > -23  AND mp3d.log_Mass_gas > 0  AND mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas > 0 GROUP BY  p.objID, s.specObjID, mp3d.mangaID, mtar.mangaID,  pcam.mstellar_median, pcam.mstellar_err,  mp3d.log_Mass, mp3d.e_log_Mass,  mp3d.log_Mass_gas, mp3d.e_log_Mass_gas,  pcam.vdisp_median, pcam.vdisp_err,  p.devRad_r, p.devRadErr_r, mp3d.re_arc, mp3d.re_kpc,  mp3d.redshift, s.z, pz.z, s.zErr,  nsa.sersic_n,  nsa.sersic_absmag_r,  nsa.sersic_ba, mp3d.ellip,   g.specsfr_tot_p50, g.sfr_tot_p50 HAVING COUNT (*) > 1 limit 2000

SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1

SELECT x.class, (1.0 * x.numEvents / x.allEvents) as ratio FROM (  SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1 ) AS x

SELECT   count(g.objid) FROM Galaxy as G JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns  ON G.objid = zns.objid  WHERE g.clean=1 and zns.nvote >= 10 and zns.p_cw > 0.8
SELECT   count(s.z) as count, p.flags  FROM photoObj p  JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  WHERE   s.class = 'galaxy'  GROUP BY   p.flags  ORDER BY  p.flags desc

SELECT   p.run, p.camcol, p.field, count(s.z) as count, avg(s.z) as average  FROM photoObj p  JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID  WHERE   s.class = 'galaxy'  and p.run = 5112   and camcol = 1   GROUP BY   p.run,p.camcol,p.field  ORDER BY  avg(s.z) desc

select  p.field, avg(s.z), count(s.z) from  PhotoObj p join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestObjID where s.class='galaxy' and p.run=5112 and p.camcol=1 group by p.run, p.camcol, p.field order by avg(s.z) desc
select  p.field, avg(s.z) from  PhotoObj p join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestObjID where s.class='galaxy' and p.run=5112 and p.camcol=1 group by p.run, p.camcol, p.field order by avg(s.z) desc
select  p.field, avg(s.z) from  PhotoObj p join SpecObj s on p.objID = s.bestObjID where s.class='galaxy' and p.run=5112 and p.camcol=1 group by p.run, p.camcol, p.field order by avg(s.z)
SELECT  count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
SELECT  count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
SELECT  count(p.objid) as num_objects FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid

select count(*) from specphoto s join stellarmassfspsgranearlydust sm on sm.specobjid=s.specobjid join zoospec zn on zn.specobjid=s.specobjid where s.z between 0.02 and 0.05 and s.class='galaxy' and s.petromag_z-5*log10(4.2*power(10.0,8)*s.z)<-19.5  and zn.uncertain=0  and s.modelmag_u-s.modelmag_r=0.25*sm.logmass-0.75  /*or s.modelmag_u-s.modelmag_r=0.25*sm.logmass-0.24 */

select count(*) from specphoto s join stellarmassfspsgranearlydust sm on sm.specobjid=s.specobjid join zoospec zn on zn.specobjid=s.specobjid where s.z between 0.02 and 0.05 and s.class='galaxy' and s.petromag_z-5*log10(4.2*power(10.0,8)*s.z)<-19.5  and zn.uncertain=0  /*and s.modelmag_u-s.modelmag_r=0.25*sm.logmass-0.75  or s.modelmag_u-s.modelmag_r=0.25*sm.logmass-0.24*/
SELECT count(*) FROM GalaxyTag p JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objID=p.objID

SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   (S.z BETWEEN 0.01 and 0.35) and   S.zwarning = 0
SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.zwarning = 0 AND s.class != 'GALAXY'
SELECT count(*)  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
SELECT count(*)  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid
SELECT  count(p.objID) FROM photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID
SELECT  count(p.objID) FROM photoObj p JOIN specObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID

select count(z) as num FROM SpecPhoto AS sp  INNER JOIN FIRST AS f ON sp.objid = f.objid  WHERE  ((z BETWEEN 0.0 AND 5)  and (class='QSO')  and (modelmag_u - modelmag_g >= -5.0)  and (modelmag_u - modelmag_g < 5.0)  and (modelmag_g - modelmag_r >= -5.0)  and (modelmag_g - modelmag_r < 5.0)  and (modelmag_r - modelmag_i >= -5.0)  and (modelmag_r - modelmag_i < 5.0)  and (modelmag_i - modelmag_z >= -5.0)  and (modelmag_i - modelmag_z < 5.0)  and (modelmag_u < 22)  and (modelmag_g < 22)  and (modelmag_r < 22)  and (modelmag_i < 22)  and (modelmag_z < 22))
SELECT   count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.zWarning=0 and s.class='GALAXY' and p.mode=1
SELECT   count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.zWarning=0 and s.class='GALAXY'
SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.zWarning=0 and s.class='GALAXY'

SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE s.zWarning=0 and s.class='QSO'

SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   ((S.class = 'GALAXY' and S. subclass = 'AGN') or S.class = 'QSO') and   SNmedian > 10 and   (S.z BETWEEN 0.01 and 0.35) and   S.zwarning = 0

SELECT count(*) FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   ((S.class = 'GALAXY' and S. subclass = 'AGN') or S.class = 'QSO') and   SNmedian > 10 and   (S.z BETWEEN 0.01 and 0.35) and   S.zwarning = 0
select s.class, count(*) FROM SpecObjAll s JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE p.clean = 1 and s.zWarning = 0 and p.expRad_r > 30 GROUP BY class
select s.class, count(*) FROM SpecObjAll s JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID WHERE p.clean = 1 and s.zWarning = 0 and s.z>4 GROUP BY class

SELECT x.class, (1.0 * x.numEvents / x.allEvents) as ratio FROM (  SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1 ) AS x

SELECT x.class, (x.numEvents / x.allEvents) as ratio FROM (  SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  ) AS allEvents  FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class  ) AS v1 ) AS x

SELECT v1.class, v1.numEvents, (  SELECT count(*) as allEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1 ) AS allEvents FROM (  SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents  FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid  WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1  GROUP BY s.class ) AS v1

SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1 GROUP BY s.class HAVING count(*) > 2000 ORDER BY numEvents limit 10
SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1 GROUP BY s.class HAVING count(*) > 2000 limit 10
SELECT s.class, count(*) as numEvents FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN SpecObj AS s on p.objid = s.bestobjid WHERE p.type = 3   AND s.z < 0.1 GROUP BY s.class limit 10
